test-method.description: TableA1-Rule1-MD_Metadata=Rule 1 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-language: documented if not defined by the encoding standard.,-characterSet: documented if ISO/IEC 10646 not used and not defined by the encoding standard.
test-method.name: checkEncodingStandard

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule2-MD_DataIdentification=Rule 2 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-characterSet: documented if ISO/IEC 10646 is not used.,-MD_Metadata.hierarchyLevel = "dataset" implies count(extent.geographicElement.EX_GeographicBoundingBox) + count(extent.geographicElement.EX_GeographicDescription) >=1.,-MD_Metadata.hierarchyLevel notEqual "dataset" implies topicCategory is not mandatory.
test-method.name: checkDataIdentification

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule3-MD_AggregateInformation=Rule 3 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-Either "aggregateDataSetName" or "aggregateDataSetIdentifier" must be documented.
test-method.name: checkAggregateInformation

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule4-MD_LegalConstraints=Rule 4 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-otherConstraints: documented if accessConstraints or useConstraints = "otherRestrictions".
test-method.name: checkLegalConstraints

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule6-DQ_Scope=Rule 6 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-" levelDescription" is mandatory if "level" notEqual 'dataset' or 'series'.
test-method.name: checkScopeOfXmlFile

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule9-MD_Georectified=Rule 9 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-"checkPointDescription" is mandatory if "checkPointAvailability" = 1.
test-method.name: checkGeorectified

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule10-MD_Band=Rule 10 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-"units" is mandatory if "maxValue" or "minValue" are provided.
test-method.name: checkBandValueOfXml

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule11-MD_Medium=Rule 11 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-"densityUnits" is mandatory if "density" is provided.
test-method.name: checkMediumOfXml

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule13-MD_ExtendedElementInformation=Rule 13 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-if "dataType" notEqual 'codelist'; 'enumeration' or 'codelistElement' then "obligation"; "maximumOccurence" and "domainValue" are mandatory.,-if "obligation" = 'conditional' then "condition" is mandatory.,-if "dataType" = 'codelistElement' then "domainCode" is mandatory.,-if "dataType" notEqual 'codelistElement' then "shortName" is mandatory.
test-method.name: checkExtendedElementInformation

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule14-EX_Extent=Rule 14 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-count(description + geographicElement + temporalElement + verticalElement) >0").
test-method.name: checkExtentValueOfXml

test-method.description: TableA1-Rule15-CI_ResponsibleParty=Rule 15 of Table A.1 ISO 19139,-count of (individualName + organisationName + positionName) > 0").
test-method.name: checkResponsiblePartyOfXml
